gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 120, Pistons 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Pistons, 120-106. The Suns were led by the 41 points and five assists and four rebounds from Kevin Durant, while Eric Gordon added 21 points and eight assists. The Pistons were led by Cade Cunningham, who had 26 points and six assists and three rebounds while Ausar Thompson totaled 14 points, nine rebounds, four blocks, and four assists. The Suns improve to 3-4 as the Pistons fall to 2-5.
